Abstract = {This paper addresses the problem of obtaining human-like motions on
   hand-arm robotic systems performing grasping actions. The focus is set
   on the coordinated movements of the robotic arm and the anthropomorphic
   mechanical hand, with which the arm is equipped. For this, human
   movements performing different grasps are captured and mapped to the
