   tasks with dual arm cooperation. A complex movement task of robot can be
   divided into action phases and subgoals, each of which corresponds to a
   dynamic motion primitive (DMP). During control of the humanoid-like dual
   arm mobile robot, there are some noises that affect the precision of the
